title: Native Instruments Reaktor 6.0 UNLOCKED [deepstatus]
description:
Native Instruments Reaktor 6.0 UNLOCKED [deepstatus]

     Modular DSP Lab
     Build custom synths, samplers, effects, and sound design tools
     Experiment with rack-style modular patching using Blocks
     Discover 70+ included instruments plus thousands of sounds
     in the User Library

     TRUE SONIC PLAYGROUND
     REAKTOR 6 is the ultimate creative toolkit for deep sound exploration,
     featuring cutting-edge DSP and high-fidelity sound.

     WHATS NEW
     REAKTOR 6 makes advanced sonic experimentation more accessible than ever.
     Primary and Core Macro libraries are refined for ease of use with new
     categories and intuitive folder structure.
     Workflows are now more efficient thanks to a modernized interface,
     improved structure editing, and a revised property and navigation.
     Plus, new features like Table Framework, Bundles, and Scoped Buses
     unlock a new level of power to REAKTOR builders.

     INTRODUCING BLOCKS
     Blocks is a new framework that turns REAKTOR 6 into a fully-equipped,
     rack-style modular synth. Over 30 Blocks ÃƒÂ± including oscillators,
     filters, effects, modulators, and sequencers ÃƒÂ± come with REAKTOR 6.
     Among these Blocks are components from acclaimed NI synths such as
     ROUNDS and MONARK ÃƒÂ± all you need to start creating elaborate modular
     synth patches.

     UNRIVALLED SOUND QUALITY
     REAKTORÃƒÂ­s trademark sound quality is unmistakable.
     From anti-aliased oscillators and ZDF (zero delay feedback) filters to
     granular synthesis engines, a team of leading developers build every
     component in REAKTOR from the core level up using the most elegant
     algorithms. Their relentless pursuit of DSP excellence keeps this sonic
     toolkit at the head of its class. And everything inside is organized for
     immediate use in REAKTORÃƒÂ­s macro libraries for fast,
     creative building sessions.

     FOR SOUND MAKERS OF ALL LEVELS
     Newcomers can quickly start playing with over 70 REAKTOR Factory
     instruments, each loaded with presets to get you started.
     Or download one of over 4,000 free instruments created by the REAKTOR
     user community. Once the REAKTOR environment becomes familiar,
     patching with Blocks unlocks a world of on-the-fly sonic experimentation.
     And for those who want to dig deeper into the creative process,
     REAKTOR lets you build complete instruments from the ground up.

     READY FOR KONTROL
     Control REAKTOR directly from a KOMPLETE KONTROL S-Series keyboard or
     MASCHINE. With the REAKTOR API, you can design fully-integrated
     performance setups. Create your own touch strip integration,
     custom displays, parameter mappings, light guide configurations,
     and more. Hybrid software/hardware instruments that are a true evolution
     in instrument design.

     POWERED BY REAKTOR
     REAKTOR is the technology platform behind some of NIÃƒÂ­s most acclaimed
     instruments and effects like RAZOR and MONARK, TRAKTOR's built-in effects,
     and the MASCHINE 2 Drum Synths. Discover the full extent of REAKTORÃƒÂ­s
     capabilities with these advanced products ÃƒÂ± all powered by REAKTOR.  




     SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS
     Windows 7, Windows 8 or Windows 10 (latest Service Pack, 32/64-bit),
     Intel Core 2 Duo or AMD AthlonTM 64 X2, 4 GB RAM.

     SUPPORTED INTERFACES
     Stand-alone, VST, Audio Units.

     Languages
      English, German, Japonese
